YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">代理商：萨奇·萨奇，伦敦</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">瑞典Tornetrask湖的冰面上，两位大胡子滑冰者在表演各种姿势的花样滑冰。不远处，裁判唱着瑞典当代音乐家Jon Henrik Fj?llgren创作的The Reindeer Herder&#39;s Joik，烘托气氛。整条广告片并未出现雷柯德酒甚至logo，却处处体现瑞典特色。该广告片出自瑞典导演 Andreas Nilsson的手笔，他曾导演Volvo著名的“一字马”广告。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=p0174jtxchy&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">夏迪（Hardys）葡萄酒：骄傲的赞助商</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">代理商：麦肯，伯明翰</p><p style