6px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">&nbsp;extends=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">&nbsp;namespace=|</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;action&nbsp;name=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;class=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;method=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">result</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;name&gt;jsp页面路径&lt;/result&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;/action&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;/package&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">P</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">ackage的name是package的名字,且是唯一的.extends是继承父package的名称.abstract是设置package的属性为抽象的,抽象的package是不能定义action.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">7.</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;global-results&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;result&nbsp;name=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;/global_result&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">全局的配置.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">8.Servlet&nbsp;API</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">1.ActionContext.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">2.action<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">搜索顺序</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">:</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">http://localhost:8080/struts2/path1/path2/student.action</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:80px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">①.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">判断</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">package</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否存在</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">:path1</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:80px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">②.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">如果不存在<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重复第一步继续查找上一级</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">package</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">路径</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如存在判断</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">action</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否存在</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</s